								<item id="item_1">felt</item>
								<item id="item_2">FELT</item>
							</acceptable>
						</typein> the cold air on his face.</p>
				</li>
				<li>
					<p>They <typein id="typein_3">
							<acceptable>
								<item id="item_1">heard</item>
								<item id="item_2">HEARD</item>
							</acceptable>
						</typein> a beast howling at night.</p>
				</li>
				<li>
					<p>I can <typein id="typein_4">
							<acceptable>
								<item id="item_1">taste</item>
								<item id="item_2">TASTE</item>
							</acceptable>
						</typein> salt in this soup.</p>
				</li>
				<li>
					<p>No one has ever <typein id="typein_5">
							<acceptable>
								<item id="item_1">seen</item>
								<item id="item_2">SEEN</item>
							</acceptable>
						</typein> the beast in the day.</p>
				</li>
			</list>
